snippet.title: Tank Blast Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Whoa! Our new game just released!
Bright and hardcore return of arcade tanks! Thunderous explosions and exciting gameplay await you on colorful levels, which are full of dastardly enemies with clever AI! Well, can you get to the end? ;)

Free download: 
http://destame.itch.io/tank-blast
